data.description: Step into a world of spaciousness and comfort as you enter this recently renovated 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven nestled on a large lot in the heart of Hauppauge. With a surplus of rooms, you'll find endless possibilities for creating a home that perfectly reflects your lifestyle, this home has the space to make that happen. The home's exterior has been recently renewed, exuding curb appeal. Inside, the basement has been transformed into a versatile living space. This home is situated in a phenomenal school district, And when it comes to location, you couldn't ask for more. Hauppauge is a sought-after town known for its vibrant community, convenient amenities, and easy access to major highways.
